wiki.content:
"Euphoria" is a track from the Swedish singer Loreen. She participated with it in Melodifestivalen 2012. The song was written by Thomas G: son and Peter Boström. On February 4, 2012 took the song on from the first semifinal and went directly to the final. On May 27, 2012, the song won the grand final of the Eurovision Song Contest 2012.
